Reserves 2MiB (or 1GiB) huge pages for inference engines (llama.cpp /
vllm / bitnet) to reduce TLB pressure.
Operator §1g: AVX-512 + 256GB RAM + ZMM ternary models \[em] all benefit
from huge-page-backed buffers.
.PP
